description: Extension to time limit for implementing planning permission W/01156/AH/07 dated 05/10/07 for Demolition of part of existing office/warehouse building including retention of front facade and partial rebuild, and erection of two to eleven storey buildings at podium level to comprise 215 residential units with 215 car parking spaces within basement, 4286sqm of Class D1 (Community Centre) on the ground and first floors with 225 associated parking spaces within the former warehouse building (at ground, mezzanine and first floor levels), 293sqm Class A3 (restaurant) on the ground floor with 5 associated car parking spaces within the basement, a landscaped courtyard at podium level with children's play area, pedestrian access from Colindale Avenue, and erection of single storey enclosures to accommodate refuse storage, cycle storage and plant machinery.
